Package com.fishsemi.sdk.aircontrol

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AirControlListener
    This interface is used to receive information and result of async request from air control service.
    DataStreamListener
    This interface is used to receive data from air board Uart and get information about Uart.
    VideoCaptureListener
    This interface is used to receive information and result of async request of video capture related operations.
    VideoStreamListener
    This interface is used to receive information of the video stream.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AirController
    This class will bind to air control service to provides control channel.
    DataStream
    This class is responsible to send and receive data from Uart on air board.
    Types
    This class contains definitions of common used types
    VideoCapture
    This class is responsible to control photo/video capture of camera system on air board.
    VideoStream
    This class is responsible to connect and display video stream of camera system on air board.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Types.CaptureMode
    Define the capture mode of air board camera system
    Types.Resolution
    Define the resolution of video stream
    Types.Result
    Define the result of async method after the request is done.
    Types.RetValue
    Define the return value of async request method
